name: CyberDefense
tagline: Teaches students in grades 7-12 principles of cyber security through a series of missions and mini games.
body:
### Cyber Defense - Cyber Security Education K7-K12
![](http://i.imgur.com/ex1wZQH.png)
Alert, Alert, Alert! 
Calling all cyber experts! We need your help.
The world is becomingly increasingly connected to the internet, as more computers come online, more threats are emerging in the realm of cyber security.

Come help our team at CyberDefense, you'll be participating with individuals from all across the world on the Blue Team to help increase defenses and mitigate attacks performed by cyber criminals.

Do you have what it takes to join our elite team of white hat hackers?
Do you love learning new things and have a sense of adventure?

If so, sign up now!
